{"tid":1201684,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"送中惡法日本各大新聞連載數日","createTime":"2019-06-11T05:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T06:07:35.000Z","uid":147203,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"42e5a7739887fba946e5740d22fb9b237b4c4a42","tid":1201684,"uid":147203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"今次100萬以上遊行已經係國際引起好大迴響。<br />\n利伸目前係日本留學，平時冇乜關心國際事項嘅日本人大部分都睇咗6月9號嘅新聞，問我詳細發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n日本唔同嘅新聞媒體都有報導相關新聞。<br />\n<br />\nNHK<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OySB28S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOySB28S.jpg&h=98756d8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9NykWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9NykWC.jpg&h=009b23ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀売<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6N8tUkS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6N8tUkS.jpg&h=47bde11a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dNneo5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dNneo5.jpg&h=a1b25b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他報社<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72Zdk1r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72Zdk1r.jpg&h=34f9e8e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wSJaofR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwSJaofR.jpg&h=3dc4b3e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每當日本人問我香港發生緊咩事，我都會向日本人解釋一個唔理100萬人上街嘅政府有幾癡撚線。<br />\n<br />\n總而言之，唔想612過後唔係香港永遠見唔到希望嘅日子。香港人加油！唔好俾暴政通過!"},{"pid":"1f7013ff6a3cdb6fc6f0bf200af04cf4b823d54a","tid":1201684,"uid":131441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ad967db69b24f1d217cad03f4e64e844180a2bf","tid":1201684,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:07:35.000Z",